- Books
- Users
- Loans
- Reservations
- Waitlist
- Reports

### Reader
- Dashboard
- Catalog
- Book Details
- My Loans
- My Reservations
- My Waitlist

---

## 10. Development Guidelines

The implementation must:

- Follow Clean Architecture (recommended)
- Keep domain logic isolated
- Use consistent English naming
- Avoid tight coupling
- Be scalable and maintainable

---

## 11. Future Enhancements

- Automatic notifications
- Multi-copy book support
- Mobile app
- QR Code check-in/out
